## **üìã API Endpoints & Testing**

### **‚úÖ Working API Endpoints**
| Endpoint | Method | Purpose | Status |
|----------|--------|---------|---------|
| `/api/payment-settings` | GET, PUT | Payment configurations | ‚úÖ Working |
| `/api/payment-credentials` | GET, POST | API keys & credentials | ‚úÖ Working |
| `/api/payment-fees` | GET, PUT | Fee structures | ‚úÖ Working |
| `/api/qr-providers` | GET, POST, DELETE | QR payment providers | ‚úÖ Working |
| `/api/onboarding-progress` | GET, PUT | Setup progress tracking | ‚úÖ Working |

### **‚ùå Missing API Endpoints (Needed)**
| Endpoint | Method | Purpose | Status |
|----------|--------|---------|---------|
| `/api/products` | GET, POST, PUT, DELETE | Product management | ‚ùå Not Implemented |
| `/api/transactions` | GET, POST, PUT | Transaction processing | ‚ùå Not Implemented |
| `/api/employees` | GET, POST, PUT, DELETE | Employee management | ‚ùå Not Implemented |
| `/api/customers` | GET, POST, PUT, DELETE | Customer management | ‚ùå Not Implemented |
| `/api/cart-sessions` | GET, POST, PUT, DELETE | Shopping cart persistence | ‚ùå Not Implemented |

