### **üö¶ Status Check Commands**
```bash
# Test all working pages
curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code} - Landing\n" http://localhost:3001/
curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code} - Register\n" http://localhost:3001/register
curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code} - Login\n" http://localhost:3001/login
curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code} - Dashboard\n" http://localhost:3001/dashboard
curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code} - POS\n" http://localhost:3001/pos
curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code} - Admin\n" http://localhost:3001/admin

# Test onboarding flow
curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code} - Welcome\n" http://localhost:3001/onboarding/welcome
curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code} - Admin Setup\n" http://localhost:3001/onboarding/admin-setup
